### VIKI Admin API - Metrics Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:14000

### Get pipeline_start_metric with default parameters (24 hours, 60 min aggregation)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric

###

### Get pipeline_start_metric with custom time range (48 hours)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric?hours_back=48

###

### Get pipeline_start_metric with custom aggregation period (30 minutes)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric?aggregation_period_minutes=30

###

### Get pipeline_start_metric with both custom parameters
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric?hours_back=12&aggregation_period_minutes=15

###

### Get metric definition for pipeline_start_metric
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric/definition

###

### List all available metrics
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/

###

### Test with a non-existent metric (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/non_existent_metric

###

### Test with invalid parameters (should return 422)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric?hours_back=200

###

### Test with invalid aggregation period (should return 422)
GET http://localhost:14000/api/v1/metrics/pipeline_start_metric?aggregation_period_minutes=2000

